data.description: Enjoy TWO living areas in this spacious home!  Formal living room with hardwood flooring and office (or bedroom or dining room) with french doors.  Huge kitchen with solid surface counters and an abundance of cabinetry.  Rock accents on breakfast bar. Skylight for natural lighting!  Den with fireplace overlooking fenced back yard. Master bedroom with very nice bathroom set up--love the double sink layout---lots of room! New HVAC 2018. Storm cellar in back yard. See agent notes for comps.
